---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" sideBarActiveItemID="about">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About</h1>

    <p class="mb-4">
      I am a mechanical engineering student focused on embedded systems and
      real-time firmware development. My work centers on designing reliable,
      deterministic systems that integrate tightly with hardware constraints.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4">
      I have experience building STM32-based firmware using FreeRTOS,
      DMA-driven peripheral communication, and structured state-machine
      architectures. I prioritize clean system design, modularity, and
      performance under resource constraints.
    </p>

    <p>
      I am particularly interested in embedded systems for aerospace,
      robotics, and high-reliability environments where hardware-software
      integration is critical.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
